[{"text": "Just a moment ago,", "start": 15.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "my daughter Rebecca texted me for good luck.", "start": 17.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "Her text said,", "start": 21.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "\"Mom, you will rock.\"", "start": 23.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "I love this.", "start": 26.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Getting that text", "start": 28.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "was like getting a hug.", "start": 30.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "And so there you have it.", "start": 32.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "I embody", "start": 35.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "the central paradox.", "start": 37.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I'm a woman", "start": 39.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "who loves getting texts", "start": 41.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "who's going to tell you", "start": 43.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that too many of them can be a problem.", "start": 45.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Actually that reminder of my daughter", "start": 48.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "brings me to the beginning of my story.", "start": 51.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "1996, when I gave my first TEDTalk,", "start": 54.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "Rebecca was five years old", "start": 58.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and she was sitting right there", "start": 60.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "in the front row.", "start": 62.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I had just written a book", "start": 64.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that celebrated our life on the internet", "start": 66.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and I was about to be on the cover", "start": 68.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "of Wired magazine.", "start": 71.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "In those heady days,", "start": 73.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "we were experimenting", "start": 75.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "with chat rooms and online virtual communities.", "start": 77.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "We were exploring different aspects of ourselves.", "start": 80.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "And then we unplugged.", "start": 84.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I was excited.", "start": 86.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "And, as a psychologist, what excited me most", "start": 88.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "was the idea", "start": 91.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that we would use what we learned in the virtual world", "start": 93.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "about ourselves, about our identity,", "start": 96.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "to live better lives in the real world.", "start": 99.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Now fast-forward to 2012.", "start": 102.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "I'm back here on the TED stage again.", "start": 105.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "My daughter's 20. She's a college student.", "start": 108.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "She sleeps with her cellphone,", "start": 111.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "so do I.", "start": 115.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "And I've just written a new book,", "start": 117.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "but this time it's not one", "start": 120.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "that will get me on the cover", "start": 123.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "of Wired magazine.", "start": 125.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "So what happened?", "start": 127.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "I'm still excited by technology,", "start": 130.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "but I believe,", "start": 133.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and I'm here to make the case,", "start": 135.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that we're letting it take us places", "start": 137.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that we don't want to go.", "start": 139.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Over the past 15 years,", "start": 141.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I've studied technologies of mobile communication", "start": 143.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and I've interviewed hundreds and hundreds of people,", "start": 146.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "young and old,", "start": 149.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "about their plugged in lives.", "start": 151.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "And what I've found", "start": 153.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "is that our little devices,", "start": 155.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "those little devices in our pockets,", "start": 157.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "are so psychologically powerful", "start": 160.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that they don't only change what we do,", "start": 162.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "they change who we are.", "start": 166.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Some of the things we do now with our devices", "start": 169.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "are things that, only a few years ago,", "start": 171.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "we would have found odd", "start": 174.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "or disturbing,", "start": 176.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "but they've quickly come to seem familiar,", "start": 178.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "just how we do things.", "start": 181.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "So just to take some quick examples:", "start": 183.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "People text or do email", "start": 186.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "during corporate board meetings.", "start": 188.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "They text and shop and go on Facebook", "start": 191.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "during classes, during presentations,", "start": 194.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "actually during all meetings.", "start": 197.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "People talk to me about the important new skill", "start": 199.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "of making eye contact", "start": 202.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "while you're texting.", "start": 204.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "(Laughter)", "start": 206.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "People explain to me", "start": 208.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that it's hard, but that it can be done.", "start": 210.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Parents text and do email", "start": 213.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "at breakfast and at dinner", "start": 215.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "while their children complain", "start": 217.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "about not having their parents' full attention.", "start": 220.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "But then these same children", "start": 222.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "deny each other their full attention.", "start": 224.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "This is a recent shot", "start": 227.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "of my daughter and her friends", "start": 229.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "being together", "start": 232.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "while not being together.", "start": 234.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "And we even text at funerals.", "start": 237.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I study this.", "start": 239.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "We remove ourselves", "start": 241.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "from our grief or from our revery", "start": 243.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and we go into our phones.", "start": 245.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Why does this matter?", "start": 248.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "It matters to me", "start": 250.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "because I think we're setting ourselves up for trouble --", "start": 252.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "trouble certainly", "start": 255.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "in how we relate to each other,", "start": 257.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "but also trouble", "start": 259.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "in how we relate to ourselves", "start": 261.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and our capacity for self-reflection.", "start": 264.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "We're getting used to a new way", "start": 267.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "of being alone together.", "start": 269.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "People want to be with each other,", "start": 272.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "but also elsewhere --", "start": 274.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "connected to all the different places they want to be.", "start": 276.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "People want to customize their lives.", "start": 279.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "They want to go in and out of all the places they are", "start": 282.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "because the thing that matters most to them", "start": 285.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "is control over where they put their attention.", "start": 287.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "So you want to go to that board meeting,", "start": 291.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "but you only want to pay attention", "start": 294.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "to the bits that interest you.", "start": 296.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "And some people think that's a good thing.", "start": 298.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "But you can end up", "start": 301.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "hiding from each other,", "start": 303.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "even as we're all constantly connected to each other.", "start": 305.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "A 50-year-old business man", "start": 308.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "lamented to me", "start": 310.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that he feels he doesn't have colleagues anymore at work.", "start": 312.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "When he goes to work, he doesn't stop by to talk to anybody,", "start": 315.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "he doesn't call.", "start": 318.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "And he says he doesn't want to interrupt his colleagues", "start": 320.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "because, he says, \"They're too busy on their email.\"", "start": 323.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "But then he stops himself", "start": 326.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and he says, \"You know, I'm not telling you the truth.", "start": 328.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I'm the one who doesn't want to be interrupted.", "start": 330.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "I think I should want to,", "start": 333.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "but actually I'd rather just do things on my Blackberry.\"", "start": 335.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "Across the generations,", "start": 339.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I see that people can't get enough of each other,", "start": 341.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "if and only if", "start": 345.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "they can have each other at a distance,", "start": 347.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "in amounts they can control.", "start": 350.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I call it the Goldilocks effect:", "start": 352.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "not too close, not too far,", "start": 355.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "just right.", "start": 358.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "But what might feel just right", "start": 360.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "for that middle-aged executive", "start": 362.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "can be a problem for an adolescent", "start": 364.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "who needs to develop face-to-face relationships.", "start": 366.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "An 18-year-old boy", "start": 370.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "who uses texting for almost everything", "start": 372.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "says to me wistfully,", "start": 375.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "\"Someday, someday,", "start": 377.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "but certainly not now,", "start": 380.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I'd like to learn how to have a conversation.\"", "start": 382.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "When I ask people", "start": 386.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "\"What's wrong with having a conversation?\"", "start": 388.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "People say, \"I'll tell you what's wrong with having a conversation.", "start": 391.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "It takes place in real time", "start": 395.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and you can't control what you're going to say.\"", "start": 398.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "So that's the bottom line.", "start": 402.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Texting, email, posting,", "start": 404.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "all of these things", "start": 407.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "let us present the self as we want to be.", "start": 409.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "We get to edit,", "start": 412.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and that means we get to delete,", "start": 414.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and that means we get to retouch,", "start": 417.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "the face, the voice,", "start": 420.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "the flesh, the body --", "start": 422.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "not too little, not too much,", "start": 424.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "just right.", "start": 427.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Human relationships", "start": 429.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "are rich and they're messy", "start": 431.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and they're demanding.", "start": 433.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "And we clean them up with technology.", "start": 435.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "And when we do,", "start": 438.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "one of the things that can happen", "start": 440.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "is that we sacrifice conversation", "start": 442.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "for mere connection.", "start": 444.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "We short-change ourselves.", "start": 446.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "And over time,", "start": 449.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "we seem to forget this,", "start": 451.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "or we seem to stop caring.", "start": 453.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "I was caught off guard", "start": 456.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "when Stephen Colbert", "start": 460.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "asked me a profound question,", "start": 462.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "a profound question.", "start": 466.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "He said, \"Don't all those little tweets,", "start": 469.26, "duration": 6.0}, {"text": "don't all those little sips", "start": 475.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "of online communication,", "start": 478.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "add up to one big gulp", "start": 481.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "of real conversation?\"", "start": 484.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "My answer was no,", "start": 488.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "they don't add up.", "start": 490.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Connecting in sips may work", "start": 492.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "for gathering discrete bits of information,", "start": 496.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "they may work for saying, \"I'm thinking about you,\"", "start": 500.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "or even for saying, \"I love you,\" --", "start": 504.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I mean, look at how I felt", "start": 506.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "when I got that text from my daughter --", "start": 508.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "but they don't really work", "start": 511.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "for learning about each other,", "start": 513.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "for really coming to know and understand each other.", "start": 515.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "And we use conversations with each other", "start": 519.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "to learn how to have conversations", "start": 523.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "with ourselves.", "start": 525.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "So a flight from conversation", "start": 527.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "can really matter", "start": 529.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "because it can compromise", "start": 531.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "our capacity for self-reflection.", "start": 533.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "For kids growing up,", "start": 535.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that skill is the bedrock of development.", "start": 537.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "Over and over I hear,", "start": 541.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "\"I would rather text than talk.\"", "start": 543.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "And what I'm seeing", "start": 546.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "is that people get so used to being short-changed", "start": 548.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "out of real conversation,", "start": 550.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "so used to getting by with less,", "start": 552.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "that they've become almost willing", "start": 555.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "to dispense with people altogether.", "start": 557.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "So for example,", "start": 559.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "many people share with me this wish,", "start": 561.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that some day a more advanced version of Siri,", "start": 563.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "the digital assistant on Apple's iPhone,", "start": 566.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "will be more like a best friend,", "start": 569.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "someone who will listen", "start": 571.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "when others won't.", "start": 573.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I believe this wish", "start": 575.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "reflects a painful truth", "start": 577.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that I've learned in the past 15 years.", "start": 579.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "That feeling that no one is listening to me", "start": 582.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "is very important", "start": 586.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "in our relationships with technology.", "start": 588.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "That's why it's so appealing", "start": 590.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "to have a Facebook page", "start": 592.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "or a Twitter feed --", "start": 594.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "so many automatic listeners.", "start": 596.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "And the feeling that no one is listening to me", "start": 599.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "make us want to spend time", "start": 602.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "with machines that seem to care about us.", "start": 604.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "We're developing robots,", "start": 607.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "they call them sociable robots,", "start": 609.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that are specifically designed to be companions --", "start": 611.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "to the elderly,", "start": 614.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "to our children,", "start": 616.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "to us.", "start": 618.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Have we so lost confidence", "start": 620.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "that we will be there for each other?", "start": 623.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "During my research", "start": 627.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I worked in nursing homes,", "start": 629.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and I brought in these sociable robots", "start": 631.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "that were designed to give the elderly", "start": 634.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "the feeling that they were understood.", "start": 636.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "And one day I came in", "start": 639.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and a woman who had lost a child", "start": 641.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "was talking to a robot", "start": 643.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "in the shape of a baby seal.", "start": 645.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "It seemed to be looking in her eyes.", "start": 648.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "It seemed to be following the conversation.", "start": 650.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "It comforted her.", "start": 653.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "And many people found this amazing.", "start": 656.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "But that woman was trying to make sense of her life", "start": 660.26, "duration": 5.0}, {"text": "with a machine that had no experience", "start": 665.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "of the arc of a human life.", "start": 668.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "That robot put on a great show.", "start": 671.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "And we're vulnerable.", "start": 673.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "People experience pretend empathy", "start": 675.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "as though it were the real thing.", "start": 678.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "So during that moment", "start": 681.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "when that woman", "start": 685.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "was experiencing that pretend empathy,", "start": 687.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "I was thinking, \"That robot can't empathize.", "start": 690.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "It doesn't face death.", "start": 693.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "It doesn't know life.\"", "start": 695.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "And as that woman took comfort", "start": 697.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "in her robot companion,", "start": 699.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I didn't find it amazing;", "start": 701.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I found it one of the most wrenching, complicated moments", "start": 703.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "in my 15 years of work.", "start": 707.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "But when I stepped back,", "start": 711.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I felt myself", "start": 713.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "at the cold, hard center", "start": 715.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "of a perfect storm.", "start": 718.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "We expect more from technology", "start": 720.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and less from each other.", "start": 723.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "And I ask myself,", "start": 726.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "\"Why have things come to this?\"", "start": 728.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "And I believe it's because", "start": 731.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "technology appeals to us most", "start": 733.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "where we are most vulnerable.", "start": 736.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "And we are vulnerable.", "start": 738.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "We're lonely,", "start": 740.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "but we're afraid of intimacy.", "start": 742.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "And so from social networks to sociable robots,", "start": 744.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "we're designing technologies", "start": 747.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that will give us the illusion of companionship", "start": 749.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "without the demands of friendship.", "start": 752.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "We turn to technology to help us feel connected", "start": 754.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "in ways we can comfortably control.", "start": 757.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "But we're not so comfortable.", "start": 760.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "We are not so much in control.", "start": 762.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "These days, those phones in our pockets", "start": 765.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "are changing our minds and hearts", "start": 768.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "because they offer us", "start": 770.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "three gratifying fantasies.", "start": 772.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "One, that we can put our attention", "start": 774.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "wherever we want it to be;", "start": 776.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "two, that we will always be heard;", "start": 778.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and three, that we will never have to be alone.", "start": 781.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "And that third idea,", "start": 784.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that we will never have to be alone,", "start": 786.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "is central to changing our psyches.", "start": 789.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Because the moment that people are alone,", "start": 791.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "even for a few seconds,", "start": 794.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "they become anxious, they panic, they fidget,", "start": 796.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "they reach for a device.", "start": 799.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Just think of people at a checkout line", "start": 801.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "or at a red light.", "start": 803.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Being alone feels like a problem that needs to be solved.", "start": 805.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "And so people try to solve it by connecting.", "start": 809.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "But here, connection", "start": 812.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "is more like a symptom than a cure.", "start": 814.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "It expresses, but it doesn't solve,", "start": 817.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "an underlying problem.", "start": 820.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "But more than a symptom,", "start": 822.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "constant connection is changing", "start": 824.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "the way people think of themselves.", "start": 826.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "It's shaping a new way of being.", "start": 828.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "The best way to describe it is,", "start": 831.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I share therefore I am.", "start": 833.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "We use technology to define ourselves", "start": 836.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "by sharing our thoughts and feelings", "start": 839.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "even as we're having them.", "start": 841.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "So before it was:", "start": 843.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I have a feeling,", "start": 845.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I want to make a call.", "start": 847.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Now it's: I want to have a feeling,", "start": 849.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "I need to send a text.", "start": 852.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "The problem with this new regime", "start": 854.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "of \"I share therefore I am\"", "start": 857.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "is that, if we don't have connection,", "start": 859.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "we don't feel like ourselves.", "start": 861.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "We almost don't feel ourselves.", "start": 863.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "So what do we do? We connect more and more.", "start": 865.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "But in the process,", "start": 868.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "we set ourselves up to be isolated.", "start": 870.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "How do you get from connection to isolation?", "start": 873.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "You end up isolated", "start": 877.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "if you don't cultivate the capacity for solitude,", "start": 879.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "the ability to be separate,", "start": 881.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "to gather yourself.", "start": 884.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Solitude is where you find yourself", "start": 886.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "so that you can reach out to other people", "start": 889.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and form real attachments.", "start": 891.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "When we don't have the capacity for solitude,", "start": 894.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "we turn to other people in order to feel less anxious", "start": 897.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "or in order to feel alive.", "start": 900.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "When this happens,", "start": 902.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "we're not able to appreciate who they are.", "start": 904.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "It's as though we're using them", "start": 907.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "as spare parts", "start": 909.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "to support our fragile sense of self.", "start": 911.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "We slip into thinking that always being connected", "start": 914.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "is going to make us feel less alone.", "start": 917.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "But we're at risk,", "start": 921.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "because actually it's the opposite that's true.", "start": 923.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "If we're not able to be alone,", "start": 926.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "we're going to be more lonely.", "start": 928.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "And if we don't teach our children to be alone,", "start": 930.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "they're only going to know", "start": 933.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "how to be lonely.", "start": 935.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "When I spoke at TED in 1996,", "start": 937.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "reporting on my studies", "start": 940.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "of the early virtual communities,", "start": 942.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I said, \"Those who make the most", "start": 944.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "of their lives on the screen", "start": 947.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "come to it in a spirit of self-reflection.\"", "start": 949.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "And that's what I'm calling for here, now:", "start": 952.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "reflection and, more than that, a conversation", "start": 955.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "about where our current use of technology", "start": 958.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "may be taking us,", "start": 961.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "what it might be costing us.", "start": 963.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "We're smitten with technology.", "start": 965.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "And we're afraid, like young lovers,", "start": 968.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "that too much talking might spoil the romance.", "start": 971.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "But it's time to talk.", "start": 974.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "We grew up with digital technology", "start": 976.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and so we see it as all grown up.", "start": 979.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "But it's not, it's early days.", "start": 981.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "There's plenty of time", "start": 984.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "for us to reconsider how we use it,", "start": 986.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "how we build it.", "start": 988.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I'm not suggesting", "start": 990.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that we turn away from our devices,", "start": 992.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "just that we develop a more self-aware relationship", "start": 994.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "with them, with each other", "start": 997.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and with ourselves.", "start": 999.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "I see some first steps.", "start": 1002.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Start thinking of solitude", "start": 1004.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "as a good thing.", "start": 1006.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Make room for it.", "start": 1008.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Find ways to demonstrate this", "start": 1010.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "as a value to your children.", "start": 1013.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Create sacred spaces at home --", "start": 1015.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "the kitchen, the dining room --", "start": 1017.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and reclaim them for conversation.", "start": 1019.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Do the same thing at work.", "start": 1022.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "At work, we're so busy communicating", "start": 1024.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that we often don't have time to think,", "start": 1026.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "we don't have time to talk,", "start": 1029.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "about the things that really matter.", "start": 1032.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Change that.", "start": 1034.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Most important, we all really need to listen to each other,", "start": 1036.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "including to the boring bits.", "start": 1040.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "Because it's when we stumble", "start": 1044.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "or hesitate or lose our words", "start": 1046.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "that we reveal ourselves to each other.", "start": 1049.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "Technology is making a bid", "start": 1053.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "to redefine human connection --", "start": 1056.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "how we care for each other,", "start": 1058.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "how we care for ourselves --", "start": 1060.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "but it's also giving us the opportunity", "start": 1062.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "to affirm our values", "start": 1064.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and our direction.", "start": 1066.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I'm optimistic.", "start": 1068.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "We have everything we need to start.", "start": 1070.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "We have each other.", "start": 1073.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "And we have the greatest chance of success", "start": 1075.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "if we recognize our vulnerability.", "start": 1078.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "That we listen", "start": 1081.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "when technology says", "start": 1083.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "it will take something complicated", "start": 1085.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and promises something simpler.", "start": 1088.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "So in my work,", "start": 1091.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I hear that life is hard,", "start": 1093.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "relationships are filled with risk.", "start": 1096.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "And then there's technology --", "start": 1098.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "simpler, hopeful,", "start": 1100.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "optimistic, ever-young.", "start": 1102.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "It's like calling in the cavalry.", "start": 1105.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "An ad campaign promises", "start": 1107.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that online and with avatars,", "start": 1109.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "you can \"Finally, love your friends", "start": 1111.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "love your body, love your life,", "start": 1115.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "online and with avatars.\"", "start": 1118.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "We're drawn to virtual romance,", "start": 1121.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "to computer games that seem like worlds,", "start": 1123.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "to the idea that robots, robots,", "start": 1126.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "will someday be our true companions.", "start": 1130.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "We spend an evening on the social network", "start": 1133.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "instead of going to the pub with friends.", "start": 1136.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "But our fantasies of substitution", "start": 1139.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "have cost us.", "start": 1141.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Now we all need to focus", "start": 1144.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "on the many, many ways", "start": 1147.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "technology can lead us back", "start": 1149.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "to our real lives, our own bodies,", "start": 1151.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "our own communities,", "start": 1154.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "our own politics,", "start": 1156.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "our own planet.", "start": 1158.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "They need us.", "start": 1160.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Let's talk about", "start": 1162.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "how we can use digital technology,", "start": 1164.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "the technology of our dreams,", "start": 1167.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "to make this life", "start": 1170.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "the life we can love.", "start": 1172.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Thank you.", "start": 1174.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "(Applause)", "start": 1176.26, "duration": 6.0}]